    <item>
      <title>随着官员考虑市场救援计划，中国股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/chinese-stocks-rebound-as-market-rescue-package-mulled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港中国股市反弹，据称政策制定者正在考虑采取一揽子措施来稳定低迷的市场，这让投资者希望遭受重创的资产类别至少能在短期内得到缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/chinese-stocks-rebound-as-market-rescue-package-mulled</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 02:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑推出2780亿美元的股市救助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-mulls-stock-market-rescue-package-backed-by-278-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国当局正在考虑采取一揽子措施来稳定暴跌的股市，此前为恢复投资者信心所做的努力未能成功，并促使李强总理呼吁采取“强有力”的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-mulls-stock-market-rescue-package-backed-by-278-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和英国对胡塞武装发动新的打击，油价保持上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国和英国对伊朗支持的也门胡塞叛乱分子进行新一轮打击后，油价保持上涨，加剧了中东紧张局势，抵消了对全球供应仍然充足的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 00:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市反弹失败，亚洲股市守住涨幅：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市大多上涨，中国股市在新的市场救助计划消息传出后上涨，但失去动力。日本央行坚持其政策后，日元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:35:03 GMT</pubDate>
